items.title: Trump signs bill ordering US justice department to release Epstein files
items.description: The bill gives the US Justice Department 30 days to release all the files in a searchable format.

items.title: US military officials in Kyiv as Europe warns against reported Russia peace plan
items.description: It comes after reports the US and Russia have prepared a 28-point peace plan, allegedly with major concessions from Ukraine.

items.title: Woman jailed for 20 years over murder of Australian surfer brothers
items.description: Ari Gisell told her boyfriend she liked the tyres on their car, instigating the carjacking that killed three surfers in Mexico last year.

items.title: Ethiopia receives historic artefacts held in Germany for 100 years
items.description: Ethiopia has welcomed the return as part of a broader push to repatriate items of national significance.

items.title: Korean coast guard arrests helmsman who was on his phone when ferry ran aground
items.description: Crew members are under investigation for possible negligence, according to the coast guard.
